By":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:29:38.000Z","msg":"我班連登仔，我係鬼都忍唔住岀嚟笑柒你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470387</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2aa6656f52fcd224a0c631640c33d7d3fe0274db","tid":1476312,"uid":66447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T20:09:12.000Z","msg":"如果真係拖 我想企係紅隧入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}